{"title":"吴王剑","authors":["燕翎"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":1,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴王剑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕翎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埋藏地下二千四百年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这柄出土的稀世名剑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时光象水一样流逝了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝剑却没有半点锈渍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁砧上锻打烈火中炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精魂一个，清纯一愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"錾上吴王显赫的剑铭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象征竞武争雄的勋业。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剑身泛一派青澄之色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"净若秋空，潮生云现，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星影依稀荡漾于水底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锋利的刃口亮如霜雪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"佩剑的霸主化为尘土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古剑却依然云霞耀焕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不朽声名属于铸剑者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那诞生于炉火的诗篇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起古剑用手指轻弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铮铮的啸鸣震撼肝胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是铸剑者壮烈心曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰然回荡在霄壤之间……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}